#. Tag: title
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning touch typing. It helps you learn to "
"type on a keyboard quickly and correctly. Every finger has it's place on the "
"keyboard with associated keys to press."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; je program za učenje slepega tipkanja. Pomaga vam, da se hitro "
"in pravilno naučite tipkati po tipkovnici. Vsak prst ima svoje mesto na "
"tipkovnici s pripadajočimi tipkami, ki jih lahko pritisne."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; helps you learn to touch type by providing you with text to "
"train on, and adjusts to different levels depending on how good you are. It "
"can display which key to press next, and correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; vam pomaga naučiti slepo tipkati, tako da vam ponudi besedilo, "
"na katerem se lahko urite, in se prilagaja različnim nivojem glede na to, "
"kako dobri ste. Lahko prikaže, katero tipko pritisniti naslednjo, in "
"uporabiti pravi prst."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "This application is part of the official &kde; education module."
msgstr "Ta aplikacija je del uradne aplikacije &kde; izobraževalni modul."

